{
  "stem": "26728.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's how all of them worked except for the ones that used decompression or, uh, carbon monoxide gas, which was the exhaust from airplane engines-- airplane motors, gas tanks, motors, truck motors, things of that nature.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, that's the story of the Dachau gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Controversy-wise, some people say it was never used.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I argue on the internet with, uh, with deniers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have read books by scholars who say it was used, not like Auschwitz or not even-- not even like Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Mauthausen had a death gas chamber that they used to kill people with on purpose.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The story of Dachau gas chamber is they used it to experiment with on animals.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They used it to experiment to get rid of crazy people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If you were-- if you went nuts, they put you in the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They could have just as well have shot you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But there are letters published in-- in, uh, scholarly books, letters between Himmler and, uh, officers at Dachau, doctors-- about experimenting with gas at Dachau and taking-- using it on human beings.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't see that swing again until I got to-- now I never did see that swing again, but you-- you had-- you had the-- you had the-- the chai-- the cuffs with the real heavy, wide steel cuffs that they bolted them on, you know?",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And about this much chain in between, so your hands were like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they would put your hands behind you and do this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They would do-- they had these poles at Dachau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There-- there were more poles at Dachau where they used with the arms behind them.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
